<doc id="972122" wikidata="Q2279640" url="?curid=972122" title="Hey Man">
<text>Hey Man is the fourth studio album by the hard rock band, Mr. Big. It would be their last album with guitarist Paul Gilbert until 2011&#x27;s &quot;What If...&quot;. The album was the most successful Mr. Big release in Japan, topping the Japanese Oricon chart, where it remained for 16 weeks.

